- It's a simple life here.

01:27.590 --> 01:30.025
Make wool. Make music.

01:30.230 --> 01:31.266
[SHEEP SCREAMS]

01:31.350 --> 01:34.741
FLEETWOOD: And that song they're playing,
it's the only one they know.

01:35.510 --> 01:37.900
