01:39.510 --> 01:43.390
And the city I came from
is a distant memory.

01:43.470 --> 01:44.506
[SHEEP SNORING]

01:44.590 --> 01:47.742
FLEETWOOD: But even in paradise,
you can't hide from trouble.

01:48.110 --> 01:51.660
