- [SHEEP SCREAMING]
- [WOLVES GROWLING]

02:07.790 --> 02:11.067
FLEETWOOD: The wolves didn't count on
Khampa's secret weapon,

02:12.470 --> 02:15.110
- [GROWLING]
- FLEETWOOD: Deadly Mastiff Paw.

02:15.750 --> 02:16.786
[SHOCKWAVE]

02:22.190 --> 02:25.786
