from deep down inside.

02:29.390 --> 02:30.426
[CHEERING, BLEATING]

02:33.870 --> 02:34.906
[SHOCKWAVE]

02:36.710 --> 02:39.020
FLEETWOOD: Linnux and his gang
were whooped so bad,

02:39.110 --> 02:41.750
we were all sure they were gone for good.

02:42.630 --> 02:44.747
But Khampa figured otherwise.

02:45.590 --> 02:48.264
- He built an army.
- [INHALES DEEPLY]

02:48.950 --> 02:51.021
And he started training Bodi.

02:52.710 --> 02:55.464
When Bodi could stay focused, that is.

02:55.550 --> 02:57.860
[MUSIC PLAYING]

03:02.990 --> 03:05.744
Well, that was the end of music
in the village.

03:05.910 --> 03:08.709
Khampa said that it was a distraction.

03:09.790 --> 03:13.101
- That we had to be vigilant.
- [SHEEP SOBBING]

03:15.030 --> 03:16.066
[LOCK CLICKS]

03:16.670 --> 03:20.300
Well, things around here
got a whole lot quieter.

03:21.110 --> 03:23.500
[PLUCKING TOVSHUUR STRING]

03:24.350 --> 03:27.502
Until one day...

03:33.830 --> 03:34.866
[GRUNTS SOFTLY]

03:35.630 --> 03:38.668
It's too bad they have to be
locked up like that.

03:38.750 --> 03:39.979
That's for sure.

03:40.070 --> 03:42.744
- Aren't you supposed to be somewhere?
- BODI: Am I?

03:42.830 --> 03:46.107
Oh! Oh, yeah, right!
See you later, Fleetwood!

03:46.710 --> 03:47.746
[CHUCKLES]

03:48.390 --> 03:50.985
You and me will check in later, huh?

