- Come on! Double time it!

05:51.430 --> 05:53.581
Let's go! Let's go! Move it, move it!

05:54.270 --> 05:55.989
Whoa, whoa, whoa! Just on backwards.

05:56.070 --> 05:59.268
Come here. Adjust. There we go.

05:59.350 --> 06:00.386
