has been making this...

06:47.310 --> 06:49.950
Squeaking noise?
Oiled it two days ago, sir.

06:50.030 --> 06:51.020
I mean, Dad.

06:51.390 --> 06:53.746
Okay, well, I'll, uh, I'll see you.

06:54.390 --> 06:55.619
[BODI WHISTLING]

06:55.710 --> 06:57.861
KHAMPA: How about your Deadly Mastiff Paw?

06:57.950 --> 06:58.940
[BODI GROANS]

06:59.630 --> 07:00.620
Get the dummy.

07:02.630 --> 07:03.666
KHAMPA: Okay.

07:03.950 --> 07:05.270
- Wolf's coming.
- Yeah.

07:05.350 --> 07:06.340
He sees you.

07:06.430 --> 07:08.069
- Oh, boy. Oh.
- Here he comes.

07:08.190 --> 07:09.180
- He's coming at you.
- Okay.

07:09.270 --> 07:10.306
- He's almost on top of you.
- Whoo!

07:10.390 --> 07:12.427
- He's in your face!
- [SHOCKWAVE]

07:14.630 --> 07:16.542
Fail! You took too long, everyone's dead.

07:16.630 --> 07:17.984
- Dad, can I just...
- Bodi, Bodi, Bodi.

07:18.070 --> 07:20.346
You gotta find the fire inside.

07:20.510 --> 07:22.024
- Find that passion.
- Yeah.

07:22.110 --> 07:23.226
Okay? Hate the wolf.

07:23.310 --> 07:25.063
- Hate wolves. Hate 'em.
- There you go.

07:25.150 --> 07:26.470
- Can't stand 'em.
- Nice.

07:26.630 --> 07:29.225
- Wanna just kick 'em!
- Use that!

07:30.790 --> 07:33.589
[BREATHING DEEPLY]

07:34.470 --> 07:36.507
[WIMPY ZING]

07:37.070 --> 07:40.188
Yes! Did you see that? Fist pump!
Double fist pump!

07:40.270 --> 07:42.705
- I hit the wolf!
- [SHEEP SENTRIES] Wolf? Wolf!

07:43.590 --> 07:45.707
Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Calm down guys! False alarm!

07:45.790 --> 07:47.986
[SHEEP SENTRIES CLAMORING]

07:51.550 --> 07:52.540
BODI: Sorry about that, Dad.

07:52.630 --> 07:54.587
Come on! Inside!
You're gonna blow our cover!

07:54.990 --> 07:56.265
SHEEP SENTRY 1: So, there's no wolf.

07:56.350 --> 07:57.579
SHEEP SENTRY 2: I guess not.

