to my roots.

11:22.550 --> 11:23.904
You know, back to where it all started.

11:23.990 --> 11:25.185
RADIO DJ: Where did it all start?

11:25.270 --> 11:28.786
ANGUS: I got my first six-string guitar
when I was a small cat.

11:29.110 --> 11:30.146
- [GRUNTS]
- [METALLIC CLANG]

11:31.270 --> 11:33.501
ANGUS: And I got on there
and the music came out,

11:33.590 --> 11:35.024
and the words, you know...

11:35.110 --> 11:36.146
[GUITAR STRINGS RESONATING]

11:36.230 --> 11:37.869
Once I started, there was no going back.

11:37.950 --> 11:40.909
- You know, I was just hooked, really.
- [GUITAR MUSIC PLAYING]

11:43.110 --> 11:44.226
[GUITAR MUSIC PLAYING]

11:56.870 --> 12:00.659
So then I came down to the city
to Rock 'n' Roll Park,

12:00.750 --> 12:04.027
'cause you know these musicians have taken
the whole thing over, mate.

12:08.030 --> 12:11.910
And I found a band there in need
of a guitar, and then the rest is history.

12:11.990 --> 12:14.459
History and geography
and a little bit of mathematics.

12:14.550 --> 12:15.586
RADIO DJ: Amazing.

12:15.990 --> 12:18.300
So any advice for up and coming musicians?

12:18.390 --> 12:21.508
ANGUS: Play your guts
out and... and never stop.

12:21.590 --> 12:25.584
Even when your dad says,
"Stop!" Don't stop.

12:26.230 --> 12:27.869
[HUMMING SOFTLY]

12:32.630 --> 12:33.859
- Dad?
- Hmm-mmm.

12:33.950 --> 12:35.623
Got some great news for you.

12:35.710 --> 12:38.066
- Got some fabulous news.
- Mm-hmm.

12:38.150 --> 12:40.506
I've decided to become a musician.

12:40.590 --> 12:42.627
[GASPS] What. Where'd you...

12:43.110 --> 12:45.341
Did you break into the... [GROANS]

12:45.430 --> 12:46.750
My son, the thief.

12:46.830 --> 12:49.823
I... I know. I'm sorry, but see,
there's this guy named Angus!

12:49.910 --> 12:52.061
And he was telling me
about Rock 'n' Roll Park,

12:52.150 --> 12:53.630
and finding my band.

12:53.710 --> 12:56.782
And it was, like, the answer
to the question of my life, Dad!

12:57.030 --> 12:59.590
- Do you understand?
- Now I'm gonna have to get a new lock.

12:59.670 --> 13:01.548
Like those things grow on trees
around here.

13:01.630 --> 13:04.589
