Hand it over. Give me the...

13:12.190 --> 13:15.547
- [GRUNTING]
- Bodi! Give me that! Give me...

13:15.630 --> 13:16.700
Come here!

13:17.350 --> 13:19.103
- [OBJECTS CLATTERING]
- Hand it to me!

13:19.630 --> 13:21.030
- [GRUNTING]
- [GUITAR MUSIC CONTINUES]

13:21.110 --> 13:22.146
[DOOR CLOSES]

13:22.590 --> 13:24.343
You're not gonna be a musician, Bodi!

13:24.430 --> 13:26.342
You're gonna be a guard.

13:26.430 --> 13:29.104
Now, when you've come to your senses,
you're going to march down here

13:29.190 --> 13:30.943
and you're going to hand over
that noisemaker,

13:31.070 --> 13:33.744
and we're going to pretend
this never happened! Agreed?

13:35.310 --> 13:37.222
I'll take your silence as a yes.

13:37.510 --> 13:39.467
[GUITAR MUSIC PLAYING]

13:40.470 --> 13:43.429
# Whoo! Yeah! #

13:44.190 --> 13:45.863
# Uh-huh! #

13:45.950 --> 13:47.907
# Yeah! #

13:48.910 --> 13:49.900
[EXCLAIMS, LAUGHS]

13:49.990 --> 13:52.983
# I like it loud I like it tight #

13:53.110 --> 13:56.262
# I like them banging
