- [STATIC CRACKLES]
- Ow!

16:26.990 --> 16:28.390
- [STATIC CRACKLES]
- Ow! [LAUGHS]

16:28.470 --> 16:29.460
[BOTH LAUGHING]

16:30.070 --> 16:31.186
